Title: The Tongan Board of Commissioners of Currency (1935-1989): Not an Orthodox Currency Board
Abstract: This paper provides a historical summary, legislative history, and the first spreadsheet data series of the Tonga Board of Commissioners of Currency (1935-1989) and uses statistical tests to examine to what extent it operated as an orthodox currency board.
