Title: Analysis of the Estonian Currency Board
Abstract: We provide a spreadsheet data series and legislative history of the Estonian currency board from 1992 to 2011. The paper assesses the level of orthodoxy exhibited by the board through statistics from annual reports. This paper makes various balance sheet data available in machine-readable form in a companion spreadsheet workbook.
